Description: Beautiful full-screen digital clock with calendar integration
 Thyme is a beautiful, full-screen digital clock application with Google 
 Calendar integration, alarms, weather display, and dynamic backgrounds.
 Perfect for Raspberry Pi kiosks, wall-mounted displays, or any always-on 
 screen.
 .
 Features include:
  * Full-screen digital clock with large, readable time and date display
  * Google Calendar integration showing upcoming events
  * Configurable alarms with visual and audio notifications
  * Weather display with beautiful icons
  * Discord integration for recent messages
  * Dynamic backgrounds with smooth fade transitions
  * Text-to-speech announcements
  * Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux)
  * Highly configurable via environment variables and config files 